BRINGING OUR YOUTH CLOSER We invite students of grades 8-11 from Volnovakha district schools on an excursion and educational trip to Russian cities. Duration of the trip is from April 15 to May 12🕐One trip time is 9 days (4 days on the road/5 excursion days)🏙Venue: St. Petersburg , Moscow, Nizhny Novgorod What will the guys get from the trip? - interesting excursions;
- visiting leading universities in St. Petersburg, Moscow and Nizhny Novgorod
- acquaintance with modern objects of Russia: Art residence in St. Petersburg, Yandex headquarters in Moscow, football stadium in Nizhny Novgorod; - meetings with interesting people: pilots, famous performers, cosmonauts, scientists, Olympic champions, Heroes of the Russian Federation;
- the opportunity to participate in intellectual interactive games in an online format. During the trip, the children will be accompanied by mentors and teachers, and medical and psychological support is also provided. Do not miss the opportunity to give your child unforgettable emotions and impressions. We are waiting for your applications from educational institutions.🇷🇺Official website of the administration🏛Head of Administration of the Volnovakha Municipal DistrictSubscribe to the channel VKontakteOdnoklassniki

